{"tid":546562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【不尊重對手？】尼馬這動作應如何解讀？","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T08:22:51.000Z","uid":8112,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f31cc51ef0f6bf5476325908df1b78dab5cfc3","tid":546562,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"昨晚一場法國聯賽盃巴黎聖日耳門vs雷恩的比賽中，坐擁天價身價的尼馬有一動作引起熱話，令人質疑他的人格。<br />\n<br />\n就在比賽尾段，聖日耳門以3：2領先對手，而對手有一位球員倒在地上，只見尼馬看似很有風度走過去伸手想扶對方起來，誰不知當對方伸手想借他的手起來之時，尼馬竟然縮手跑開，並面帶笑容的好像完成一次惡作劇的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n作為一位足球巨星，尼馬這個行為確實有失身份，令人感覺他像在玩弄對手一樣，更何況當時球隊正領先對手，這樣做明顯是對對方的一種不尊重。<br />\n<br />\n其實外界一直對於尼馬的技術有充分的肯定，唯獨他的態度好似還沒有很成熟，令人感覺他還沒有足夠的領軍能力，這實在令人失望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=1bCnYANIJHA&amp;time_continue=33&amp;ebc=ANyPxKpoc1v-GYWWaTa0kHk4pTXuSuWkyVV973YQRyvB9FNMRKL5ST2hIrc9-_ar1l0qcSWwnhNvoG-FmnxFsXtatJIXNAgYkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1bCnYANIJHA%26time_continue%3D33%26ebc%3DANyPxKpoc1v-GYWWaTa0kHk4pTXuSuWkyVV973YQRyvB9FNMRKL5ST2hIrc9-_ar1l0qcSWwnhNvoG-FmnxFsXtatJIXNAgYkA&d=J%2BGjt9OVN8jpNQuOpJCvzzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=28c42c5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=1bCnYANIJHA&amp;time_continue=33&amp;ebc=ANyPxKpoc1v-GYWWaTa0kHk4pTXuSuWkyVV973YQRyvB9FNMRKL5ST2hIrc9-_ar1l0qcSWwnhNvoG-FmnxFsXtatJIXNAgYkA</a><br />\n0:27<br />\n<br />\n好撚仆街 咁樣撚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17df99c51b7f2ccc72a75814c3fb3a421856e4b3","tid":546562,"uid":105121,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"巴塞冇咗佢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685e3a6b0fac73dd48506f9e6ae98282b8ac73dd","tid":546562,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm